name: noaa-esri-shapefile-sediment-composition-class-predictions-in-new-york-offshore-planning-area-41f75
notes: This dataset represents sediment composition class predictions from a sediment spatial model developed for the New York offshore spatial planning area. The predictive spatial model of mean grain size was developed building upon the data compilation and analytical framework laid out by Goff et al. (2008) and Poppe et al. (2005).
